name: QR Usage Report
query:
SELECT 
    target_doctype as "DocType:Link:200",
    target_name as "Document:Dynamic Link:200",
    qr_type as "QR Type:Data:120",
    status as "Status:Data:100",
    scan_count as "Scans:Int:80",
    created_on as "Created:Datetime:150",
    last_scanned as "Last Scan:Datetime:150"
FROM `tabQR Link`
ORDER BY scan_count DESC, created_on DESC
